"role.sonarU.doc" : "Places antennas that detect kills."
"role.sonarU.ability.title" : "Unique Ability "Antenna""
"role.sonarU.ability.main" : "Can place antennas.<br>If a kill happens near an antenna, all players are notified by a noise."
