"role.sonarU.ability.antenna" : "<title>Antenna</title>An active antenna. Notifies when a kill occurs nearby."
"role.sonarU.ability.break" : "<title>Broken Antenna</title>An antenna breaks the first time it detects a kill.<br>Broken antennas can no longer detect kills."
　
